com.pse.testserver.entities

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pse.testserver.entities.Event

  • @Entity
public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    Entity class for the persisted event data from the "events" table. Represents an event, providing access to the event's unique id, name, description, category, subcategory, creator, profile picture url and participants .
